#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:2
msgid "镜像"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:5
msgid "基本概念"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:6
msgid "Docker 镜像可以看作是一个特殊的文件系统，用于提供容器运行时所需的文件，同时镜像还包含了一些为运行时准备的一些信息（环境变量、用户等）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:8
msgid "在构建之后镜像不会被改变，即是说镜像中不会包含动态的数据。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:11
msgid "Windows 镜像"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:12
msgid ""
"由于 Windows 并不直接开放 syscall ，所有的 Windows 程序都必须通过 sys dll 与内核沟通，这就导致 Windows"
" 镜像并不能直接通过 scratch 来构建，只能基于微软提供的几个基础镜像来构建。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:14
msgid "镜像包括："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:16
msgid ""
"`windows servercore <https://hub.docker.com/_/microsoft-windows-"
"servercore>`_ 功能最完整，包含传统的 .net framework 环境"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:17
msgid ""
"`windows nanoserver <https://hub.docker.com/_/microsoft-windows-"
"nanoserver>`_ 包含 .net core 运行环境"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:18
msgid ""
"`windows <https://hub.docker.com/_/microsoft-windows>`_ 提供完整的 windows "
"server api，正在被 windows server 替代"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cloud/docker/image.rst:19
msgid ""
"`windows server <https://hub.docker.com/_/microsoft-windows-server/>`_ "
"提供完整的 windows server api"
msgstr ""
